        q: 'What does The Fool mean for a new relationship?',
        a: `For a new relationship, The Fool is one of the most promising openers in the deck. It suggests genuine compatibility around play, curiosity, and the willingness to discover each other slowly rather than slot the connection into a familiar template. There may be a sense of being lifted out of your normal rhythm — travel, a different social world, a quality of lightness you had almost forgotten. The honest caution is to honour the early stage as an early stage. Don't fast-forward the timeline or import old anxieties. Let the relationship surprise you. The Fool rewards presence over planning, especially in the opening weeks.`,
